trackedEntityAttributes.name: Age
trackedEntityAttributes.description:
Please use this data element to indicate the age of the patient. 
You can either:
- enter the date of birth, and the age will be automatically calculated, based on the date of today
- enter the age in years, months and days, as precisely as possible, and an approximate date of birth will be calculated.
This data element is "dynamic", which means that the patient will be one day older everyday in the database.
